     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb n="18" facs="11"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <hi>You friendly Readers heare,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>how that this foolish Prelate,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>Poore peoples eyes would bleare</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>with fabl's he doth relate,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>In stead of giuing glory</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>to God, and Christ our hope,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>To trust in his false story,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>and Pardons of the Pope,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>And that to get forgiuing</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>of their offences all,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>The way is to beleeue in</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>and on deafe Saints to call.</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>It's time to open your eyes,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>you of the popish faction,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>Truth makes men bold and wise,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>
         <hi>crownes with successe each action.</hi>
      </l>
   </lg>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
   <pb facs="11"/>
   <pb facs="12"/>
